                   <td valign="top" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><p><STRONG><SPAN lang="EN-US">Completion of Scheduled HKIX Network Switch Ports   Relocation work</SPAN></STRONG></p>
                     <p><SPAN lang="EN-US">It was completed at 0800 HKT (GMT+8) on 18 Aug   2013.</SPAN></p></td>
